  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"Fighting for Land\" </strong>is a casual roguelite tower defense game blending randomized cards, power-ups, and territory-coloring. Randomly generated enemies and dynamic events will assault your structures and invade your land. Build defensive towers to protect your base, fight back against monsters, and dominate the battlefield by coloring all territory blocks to claim ultimate victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‌<strong>Core Gameplay Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✦ ‌<strong>Territory Coloring </strong>✦</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defensive towers not only attack monsters but also expand your influence through ‌<strong>\"territory coloring\"</strong>‌ – the core victory mechanic! Only by dyeing the entire map with your color can you fully crush the enemy forces!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402180/extras/82b514bbec1d5fa0bddeca3a44a1aa3c.avif?t=1748682973\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402180/extras_big/82b514bbec1d5fa0bddeca3a44a1aa3c.avif?t=1748682973 width=800 height=434 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✦ ‌<strong>Card-Based Tactics</strong>‌ ✦</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every card holds unique strategic effects. Precise card selection during ever-shifting battles becomes the key to victory. The game randomly generates combinations from your deck – choose optimal synergies based on real-time combat and strategic needs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402180/extras/586d57f4973b880c6ff82a001a763280.avif?t=1748682973\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402180/extras_big/586d57f4973b880c6ff82a001a763280.avif?t=1748682973 width=800 height=434 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✦ ‌<strong>Mystery Item System</strong>‌ ✦</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Randomly refreshed Mystery Shops offer tower-boosting buffs and enemy-debilitating tactical gear. A single game-changing item might reverse desperate situations during special enemy offensives!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402180/extras/4751f5a048b47edc0241f80d132c419f.avif?t=1748682973\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402180/extras_big/4751f5a048b47edc0241f80d132c419f.avif?t=1748682973 width=800 height=434 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✦ ‌<strong>Revolutionary Building Mechanics</strong>‌ ✦</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shatter traditional tower defense rules! Structures can only be deployed on colored territory, while ‌<strong>\"non-building cards\"</strong>‌ freely occupy unobstructed areas, enabling 3D defense networks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402180/extras/fa4a5945c01c974eff77b86c699916b8.avif?t=1748682973\" width=376 height=126 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✦ ‌<strong>Dynamic Special Events</strong>‌ ✦</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience multi-layered random events – unpredictable raid types, attack coordinates, and chain reactions triggered by real-time battlefield conditions. Only adaptable strategies can overcome these crises!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402180/extras/d4fac7db716bfa2f3f4c8277a8d9e284.avif?t=1748682973\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402180/extras_big/d4fac7db716bfa2f3f4c8277a8d9e284.avif?t=1748682973 width=800 height=378 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402180/extras/75faa6cdde3f51f121a57d8f4f8e5986.avif?t=1748682973\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402180/extras_big/75faa6cdde3f51f121a57d8f4f8e5986.avif?t=1748682973 width=800 height=372 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402180/extras/06e7a14c8cc3a3d9dea68d93a565a1c3.avif?t=1748682973\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402180/extras_big/06e7a14c8cc3a3d9dea68d93a565a1c3.avif?t=1748682973 width=800 height=370 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"Fighting for Land\" </strong>is a casual roguelite tower defense game blending randomized cards, power-ups, and territory-coloring. Randomly generated enemies and dynamic events will assault your structures and invade your land. Build defensive towers to protect your base, fight back against monsters, and dominate the battlefield by coloring all territory blocks to claim ultimate victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‌<strong>Core Gameplay Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✦ ‌<strong>Territory Coloring </strong>✦</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defensive towers not only attack monsters but also expand your influence through ‌<strong>\"territory coloring\"</strong>‌ – the core victory mechanic! Only by dyeing the entire map with your color can you fully crush the enemy forces!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402180/extras/82b514bbec1d5fa0bddeca3a44a1aa3c.avif?t=1748682973\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402180/extras_big/82b514bbec1d5fa0bddeca3a44a1aa3c.avif?t=1748682973 width=800 height=434 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✦ ‌<strong>Card-Based Tactics</strong>‌ ✦</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every card holds unique strategic effects. Precise card selection during ever-shifting battles becomes the key to victory. The game randomly generates combinations from your deck – choose optimal synergies based on real-time combat and strategic needs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402180/extras/586d57f4973b880c6ff82a001a763280.avif?t=1748682973\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3402180/extras_big/586d